      },
      "writtenOn": "2019-03-29T00:29:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "thanks for catching this, and yuck, it\u0027s hard to use goroutines safely with synchronous APIs. :-(\n\ni think i have this working properly now (with another pipe, but with the write end watched by epoll and the read end closed by close() -- not sure if this is what you meant, but it seems nice since it mirrors what we\u0027re doing with writeFD)",
